room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent: Stealth Force" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
room_description: A new foe has arrived and they're already planning something terrible! Only the best of the best, you and your fellow agents of Stealth Force, will be able to stop them. Infiltrate Dark Command's central bunker and stop the impending missile strike against the US. Escape undetected or we will disavow any knowledge of Stealth Force and its orders.
